{"tid":2144541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"制裁名單係有12人,冇中文名嗰1個邊個嚟?","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T12:12:50.000Z","uid":222747,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a198ea1be3b9b00e9737aa2af295388c6eb459c","tid":2144541,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/OFAC-Enforcement/Pages/20200807.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.treasury.gov%2Fresource-center%2Fsanctions%2FOFAC-Enforcement%2FPages%2F20200807.aspx&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=96e96c3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/OFAC-Enforcement/Pages/20200807.aspx</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\">SOULEYMANE</span>, Bi Sidi (a.k.a. ABASS, Sidiki; a.k.a. ABBAS, Sidiki; a.k.a. BI SIDI, Souleymane; a.k.a. SIDIKI, Abbas; a.k.a. SOULEMAN, Bi Sidi; a.k.a. SOULEMANE, Bi Sidi; a.k.a. SOULIMANE, Sidiki Abass; a.k.a. &quot;Sidiki&quot;), Central African Republic; DOB 20 Jul 1962; POB Bocaranga, Ouham-Pende prefecture, Central African Republic; nationality Central African Republic; alt. nationality Chad; alt. nationality Cameroon; Gender Male (individual) [CAR].<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">SOULEYMANE</span>咩人來的?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvEJSUM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqvEJSUM.png&h=010b2269&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今次白宮Press Releases 係一次過UPLOAD呢2篇的。<br />\n入去望望嚇一跳:<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fsm1087&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=3d37c486\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1087</a><br />\nSouleymane leads the Central African Republic (CAR)-based militia group Return, Reclamation, Rehabilitation (3R), which <span class=\"red\">has killed, tortured, raped, or displaced thousands of people since 2015. Souleymane himself has also directly participated in torture.</span> <br />\nGoogle Translate: <span class=\"red\">自2015年以來已經殺害，折磨，強姦或流離失所的數千人。蘇萊曼本人也直接參與了酷刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">將一個中非共和國嘅武裝屠夫領袖同中共港共官員放埋一齊係咩意思呀?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5ac735a3818d1cbc40df66fd9a514183e39cfaa9","tid":2144541,"uid":322642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"一樣意思"},{"pid":"486c06e3a4fa59db1c08b244b68f11beaf39462f","tid":2144541,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf25a99d2b14e48682654378b896d68c794f6b3","tid":2144541,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64287c7a8f299bf3de5678bea37d24f744aec45e","tid":2144541,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b0a59a250608cddf65be15e301cc2f92db9d9a","tid":2144541,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"幫你推埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c638b3e652ee5a1746fdcb48bc61365de4248df0","tid":2144541,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" 